currentDoc:
Are We Being Bad Citizens If We Don't Keep Up With the News?

In your opinion, are we being bad citizens if we don't keep up with the news? Do you think all people have some responsibility to know what is going on in the world? Does engaging with current events actually do anything at all? Why do you think the way you do?

---

In my opinion,

currentSuggestions.original: Citizenship is your privilege, not your right.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Citizenship is your privilege, not your right.

currentSuggestions.original: Think about the vast diversity of cultures across our nation, that is what we have to celebrate.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Think about the vast diversity of cultures across our nation, that is what we have to celebrate.

currentSuggestions.original: We can't make informed choices if we don't know who to listen to and who is telling us the truth.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: We can't make informed choices if we don't know who to listen to and who is telling us the truth.

currentSuggestions.original: Look up the bill and read it, see what the legislation actually does.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Look up the bill and read it, see what the legislation actually does.

currentSuggestions.original: We must watch out in detail.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: We must watch out in detail.

currentSuggestions.original: Don't be too lazy to participate, or it will be your ashes that are in the wind.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Don't be too lazy to participate, or it will be your ashes that are in the wind.

ops.insert: We can't make informed choices if we don't know who to listen to and who is telling us the truth.

currentSuggestions.original: Don't allow yourself to be swept into voting for someone because of a celebrity's endorsement or a slogan.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Don't allow yourself to be swept into voting for someone because of a celebrity's endorsement or a slogan.

currentSuggestions.original: Ask questions of your local candidates.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Ask questions of your local candidates.

currentSuggestions.original: Is there a manipulation of the voting?
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Is there a manipulation of the voting?

currentSuggestions.original: Find out the candidates, positions and policies.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Find out the candidates, positions and policies.
